'''莊拿芬·馬克·"祖尼"·侯臣'''（{{lang-en|'''Jonathan Mark 'Jonny' Howson'''}}，{{bd|1988年|5月21日|catIdx=H}}），簡稱'''莊拿芬·侯臣'''（{{lang-en|'''Jonathan Howson'''}}），是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[中場|中場]]，亦可擔任右翼及[[足球前鋒|前鋒]]，出身自[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]青訓系統，現時效力[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]。

他生於{{Link-en|莫利 (西約克郡)|Morley, West Yorkshire|莫利}}，並曾就讀於莫利維多利亞小學（Morley Victoria Primary School）和{{Link-en|畢格列夫高校|Bruntcliffe High School}}。侯臣在青年球隊祖奴爾獅子（Churwell Lions）展開其足球生涯，其後才在列斯聯展開其職業生涯。

==生平==
=== 球會 ===
;列斯聯
侯臣與[[占士·米拿|占士·米拿]]、[[丹尼·路斯|丹尼·路斯]]和[[艾朗·連儂|艾朗·連儂]]一同上位，他在2006年前成為列斯聯預備組的正選成員，並在這個級別取得了數次入球。2006年8月22日，侯臣雖然獲分派了33號球衣並在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]對[[車士打城足球會|車士打]]的賽事中擔任後備，但並未有上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2006-08-22| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/5266278.stm| title =Leeds 1-0 Chester| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2016-03-07| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160307111512/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/5266278.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。9月18日，侯臣與球會簽訂了三年合約，將自己的前途抵押給這支兒時愛隊<ref name=LUFC1>{{en}}{{cite web| title =Big Deal For Jonny| work =Leeds United| publisher =Leeds United| date =2006-09-18| url =http://www.leedsunited.com/page/NewsroomDetail/0,,10273~898941,00.html| accessdate =2006-09-18| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20070929094318/http://www.leedsunited.com/page/NewsroomDetail/0,,10273~898941,00.html| archivedate =2007-09-29}}</ref>

9月20日，侯臣在對[[班列特足球會|班列特]]的賽事中處子上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2006-09-19| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/5351626.stm| title =Leeds 3-1 Barnet| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2006-10-11| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20061011011744/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/5351626.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。賽後，讓侯臣上陣的時任領隊{{Link-en|奇雲·布力維爾|Kevin Blackwell}}迅速被會方解僱。新領隊[[丹尼斯·韋斯|丹尼斯·韋斯]]讓他在12月對[[侯城足球會|侯城]]賽事中首次聯賽上陣，賽後他被選為賽事最佳球員<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2006-12-23| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6185489.stm| title =Leeds 0-0 Hull| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2016-03-07| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160307140326/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6185489.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。此外，他贏得丹尼斯·韋斯和時任副隊長[[沙恩·戴利|沙恩·戴利]]的讚賞。2007年2月，他在對[[諾域治足球會|諾域治]]的賽事中攻入其加盟以來的首個入球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2007-02-03| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6305265.stm| title =Norwich 2-1 Leeds| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2007-02-12| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070212170325/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6305265.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

2007/08球季初，侯臣獲得新領隊[[加利·麥亞里士打|加利·麥亞里士打]]的重用，並成為正選球員。2008年5月，他在[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]附加賽對[[卡素爾聯足球會|卡素爾]]的賽事中攻入了兩個著名的入球，使球會打進了在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]舉行的決賽<ref name=claridgeonhowson>{{en}}{{cite web| publisher =The Guardian| date =19 May 2009| url =http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2300578/Leeds-Wembley-bound-after-Howson-strike.html| title =Leeds Wembley-bound after Howson strike| accessdate =24 September 2009| archive-date =2015-05-29| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150529164039/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2300578/Leeds-Wembley-bound-after-Howson-strike.html| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2008-05-18| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7393761.stm| title =Carlisle 0-2 Leeds (agg 2-3)| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2008-05-20| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20080520110543/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7393761.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。然而，侯臣由於未能盯緊[[占士·希達|占士·希達]]而使他協助[[唐卡士打足球會|唐卡士打]]勝出賽事<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2008-05-25| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7418498.stm| title =Doncaster 1-0 Leeds| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2009-09-27| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090927014245/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7418498.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。球季結束後，他被選為列斯聯年度最佳青年球員和球迷最佳青年球員<ref name=howsoncarlisle>{{en}}{{cite web| publisher =The Telegraph| date =16 May 2008| url =http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/blog/2009/may/19/steve-claridge-jonathan-howson-leeds| title =Steve Claridge on Leeds United's Jonathan Howson| accessdate =24 September 2009| archive-date =2009-05-22| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090522093036/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/blog/2009/may/19/steve-claridge-jonathan-howson-leeds| dead-url =no}}</ref>。他的表現亦為他贏得一份新的三年合約，如果球隊能升班至[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]會再與其續約<ref>{{en}}{{cite web  | publisher =BBC Sport  | date =20 June 2008  | url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7465388.stm  | title =Howson agrees new Leeds contract  | accessdate =2010-03-05  | archive-date =2012-01-20  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20120120214124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7465388.stm  | dead-url =no  }}</ref>。

2008/09球季初，侯臣陷入了生涯的低潮。天才球員[[法比安·迪夫|法比安·迪夫]]的出現，使他的上陣次數減少。當[[西蒙·加利臣|西蒙·加利臣]]接任列斯聯領隊後，侯臣出任中場中；法比安·迪夫則擔任左翼。2009年2月，他在對[[車頓咸足球會|車頓咸]]的賽事中[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]，以2-0的比分擊敗對手，這顯示出他的全面回歸<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2009-02-21| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7886236.stm| title =Leeds 2-0 Cheltenham| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2009-02-23| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090223172707/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7886236.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。他逐漸確立其正選位置。他整個球季主要與[[尼爾·基爾堅尼|尼爾·基爾堅尼]]一同鎮守中路，他在季後對[[米禾爾足球會|米禾爾]]的附加賽中正選上陣，然而也鎩羽而歸<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2009-05-09| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8034406.stm| title =Millwall 1-0 Leeds| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2009-05-11| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090511224252/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8034406.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2009-05-14| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8038226.stm| title =Leeds 1-1 Millwall (agg 1-2)| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2009-05-19| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090519011827/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8038226.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

2009年8月，由於隊長[[李察·尼萊|李察·尼萊]]缺陣，侯臣被任命為列斯聯的副隊長<ref name=howsonskipper>{{en}}{{cite web| publisher =Yorkshire Evening Post| date =2 September 2009| url =http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/Leeds-United-Jonny39s-pride-at.5608342.jp| title =Jonny's pride at captaincy role| accessdate =24 September 2009| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20091006205801/http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/Leeds-United-Jonny39s-pride-at.5608342.jp| archive-date =2009-10-06| dead-url =yes}}</ref>。2009/10球季，侯臣表現不俗，他與拍擋[[米高·杜爾尼|米高·杜爾尼]]建立起穩固的中場線，並帶領球隊在各項賽事中總共取得9連勝。他在對卡素爾的賽事中由於隊長復出而失去了隊長臂章。

侯臣在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]對[[奧咸足球會|奧咸]]的賽事中以一記漂亮的左腳遠射取得該季的第二個入球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2009-11-07| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8341122.stm| title =Oldham   0 - 2   Leeds United| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2009-11-09| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20091109055828/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8341122.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。當[[巴特利·莊臣|巴特利·莊臣]]受傷後，尼爾·基爾堅尼取回正選位置，這意昧著侯臣需要擔任右翼，中路則有米高·杜爾尼和尼爾·基爾堅尼搭檔。1月3日，他在足總盃對[[曼聯足球會|曼聯]]的賽事中交出助攻予[[謝美伊·碧福特|謝美伊·碧福特]]，後者不負所託取得入球，從而首次在這階段淘汰了這支衛冕[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]冠軍的球隊<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2010-01-04| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8433901.stm| title =Man Utd   0 - 1   Leeds United| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2010-04-15| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20100415091513/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8433901.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

侯臣在對[[韋甘比足球會|韋甘比]]的賽事早段時以一記遠射取得其該季的第三個入球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web| date =2010-01-09| url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8428611.stm| title =Leeds United   1 - 1   Wycombe| work =BBC Sport| accessdate =2010-03-05| archive-date =2010-01-14| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20100114072325/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8428611.stm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。2010年1月23日，他在對[[熱刺足球會|熱刺]]的足總盃賽事中出任右翼，最終雙方2-2打成平手。

;諾域治
2012年1月24日侯臣轉投[[英超|英超]]球會[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]，沒有透露轉會費，簽約三年半<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/16610340.stm |title=Norwich City sign Jonny Howson from Leeds United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-01-24 |accessdate=2012-01-25 |archive-date=2012-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124174906/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/16610340.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
2011年2月7日由於大量球員因傷退隊，侯臣獲補選首次加入[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]備戰對[[義大利21歲以下國家足球隊|義大利]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9385897.stm |title=Chelsea's Josh McEachran called into England Under-21s |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-02-07 |accessdate=2011-02-08 |archive-date=2011-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110207202144/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9385897.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，翌日獲派下半場後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9391403.stm |title=Italy U21s 1-0 England U21s |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-02-08 |accessdate=2011-02-09 |archive-date=2011-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211053644/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9391403.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

